4. UI Standardized: Card headers follow [Status] [Arrow] [Cog] layout.
5. Icon Movement: nav-arrow and chip-arrow move dynamically on hover.
6. Layout Fixes: Fixed card title cutoff (ellipsis) and chip wrapping (horizontal scroll).
7. Theme Toggle: Positioned to the right of the Privacy Switch.
8. Redlib Health: Fixed issue where Portainer reported 'Unhealthy' due to 403 errors. Updated healthcheck to ignore 403s.
9. Update Engine: Added manual "Check for Updates" button and backend logic.
10. All Updates: Added a permanent 'Update All Services' button that triggers both global image updates (Watchtower) and source code refreshes.
11. Material Design 3: Verified full compliance with M3 tokens (color, shape, motion), expressive elevations, and typography.
12. Backup Safeguards: Updates (individual or global) now trigger automated backups via migrate.sh to prevent data loss.
13. Progress Monitoring: Update progress is logged in real-time to the dashboard's log view.
14. Resource Awareness: Added UI warnings informing users about increased CPU/RAM usage during update builds.
15. Wizard Removed: Completely stripped the Setup Wizard (HTML/CSS/JS) to prevent UI interference.

DASHBOARD COG FUNCTIONALITY:
==========================================================
